overview: Adult entertainment studio, Elegant Angel, is proud to announce its latest production, Performers of the Year 2009. It features 8 scenes, and stars some of the biggest names of the year: Jenna Haze, Alexis Texas, Gianna, Sunny Lane, Shyla Stylez, Rebeca Linares, Bobbi Starr, and the beautiful 2008 breakout star, Kristina Rose!
title: Performers of the Year 2009
